			"description": "AI Interview Coach (docs/product/interview). Chat interview: start a session, submit each answer (evaluated on submit, 0-100 rubric), then complete to aggregate the final report. Bilingual (en|ru). All routes are JWT-protected and scoped to the caller.",
			"item": [
				{
					"name": "List Interviews",
					"request": {
						"method": "GET",
						"header": [],
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{API_URL}}/interviews?page=1&limit=10",
